e},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_071816_c69d527d.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"This engine comes nestled within a trellis-style frame that incorporates both steel and aluminium\",\"alt_text\":\"QJ Motor SRK 421 RR right side profile\",\"sequence\":3,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_071820_e3dc87e8.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"The SRK 421 RR is available in two colours - Red/Silver and Black\",\"alt_text\":\"QJ Motor SRK 421 RR left front three quarter studio shot\",\"sequence\":4,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_071828_895ff755.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"It comes with a 808mm tall seat\",\"alt_text\":\"QJ Motor SRK 421 RR seat \",\"sequence\":5,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_071834_59d731e4.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Braking duties are handled by Brembo\",\"alt_text\":\"QJ Motor SRK 421 RR suspension\",\"sequence\":6,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_071838_63727354.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"It comes with a 5-inch TFT with two riding modes\",\"alt_text\":\"QJ Motor SRK 421 RR TFT dash\",\"sequence\":7,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-images/qj-motor-srk-421-rr-image-gallery-440153\",\"author\":\"Ved Janve\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Ved-Janve.jpg\",\"description\":\"\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-06T07:33:53.979748+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-06T07:34:03+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T07:34:03.855492+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Bikes\",\"images_count\":7},{\"id\":440152,\"heading\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 Image Gallery\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063142_a48c7289.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063142_a48c7289.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"In 2024, the TVS Apache RR310 received mechanical upgrades, some new styling elements, and a ton of features.\",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 Static shot on track showing its design elements like aerodynamic winglets.\",\"sequence\":1,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063246_bf75b062.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"There are three colour options on offer depending on the variant you pick. \",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 All three colours panning shot on track.\",\"sequence\":2,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063253_fb70b8d8.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Currently, this limited edition colour scheme is also on offer.\",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 Limited Edition Colour\",\"sequence\":3,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063304_e7dc1ec1.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Mechanical upgrades include a lighter forged piston, an improved piston ring design, and a larger airbox to name a few. The power output has increased to 38hp and 29Nm. Additionally, it now gets a neat-looking transparent clutch cover.\",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 Transparent Clutch Cover Shot.\",\"sequence\":4,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063326_8d10bbf2.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"The Dynamic Pro kit brings in a host of electronic rider aids including RT-DSC (Race Tuned Dynamic Stability Control). This includes cornering traction control, ABS, cruise control, and wheelie control.\",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 dashboard shot static.\",\"sequence\":5,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_063413_753e6b7d.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"The switchgear is user friendly and makes it easy to operate the various features on the dash.\",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 Switchgear shot.\",\"sequence\":6,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260306_065110_24822921.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"The bike is priced starting at Rs 2.59 lakh (ex-showroom, Mumbai)\",\"alt_text\":\"TVS Apache RR 310 rear three fourth static image on track.\",\"sequence\":7,\"use_as_thumbnail\":false}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-images/tvs-apache-rr-310-image-gallery-440152\",\"author\":\"Azaman Chothia\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Azaman.jpg\",\"description\":\"\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-06T07:10:46.650516+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-06T07:10:53+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T07:28:14.217229+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Bikes\",\"images_count\":7},{\"id\":440150,\"heading\":\"Hero Xoom 160 colours image gallery\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_100054_4759a110.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_100054_4759a110.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Hero Xoom 160 is available in a single-variant with a total of 4 colour options\",\"alt_text\":\"Hero Xoom 160 front three quarter real-life shot\",\"sequence\":1,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_100058_23daea51.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Matte Rainforest Green\",\"alt_text\":\"Hero Xoom 160 front three quarter green\",\"sequence\":2,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use