t\":\"Side studio profile of Royal Enfield Super Meteor 650 first photo\",\"sequence\":1,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_082103_902f6ecf.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Astral Green\",\"alt_text\":\"Side studio profile of Royal Enfield Super Meteor 650 Astral Green\",\"sequence\":2,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_082119_c690a1bf.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Interstellar Grey\",\"alt_text\":\"Side studio profile of Royal Enfield Super Meteor 650 Interstellar Grey\",\"sequence\":3,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_082129_bda241ad.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Interstellar Green\",\"alt_text\":\"Side studio profile of Royal Enfield Super Meteor 650 Interstellar Green\",\"sequence\":4,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_082147_f42dd735.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Celestial Blue\",\"alt_text\":\"Side studio profile of Royal Enfield Super Meteor 650 Celestial Blue\",\"sequence\":5,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260305_082156_628355ec.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"Celestial Red\",\"alt_text\":\"Side studio profile of Royal Enfield Super Meteor 650 Celestial Red\",\"sequence\":6,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-images/royal-enfield-super-meteor-650-colours-image-gallery-440149\",\"author\":\"Autocar India Team \",\"author_image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/authors/images/default.png\",\"description\":\"\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-05T08:28:15.305258+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-05T08:28:31+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T08:28:31.611638+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Bikes\",\"images_count\":6},{\"id\":440148,\"heading\":\"VinFast’s Lac Hong 800S image gallery \",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_113445_a07c2cb7.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_113445_a07c2cb7.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S front quarter\",\"caption\":\"The 800S features a chrome strip in its profile that visually connects the DRLs with the tailights. \",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S front quarter\",\"sequence\":1,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_113455_2f9289bb.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S front design\",\"caption\":\"It gets a gold-plated hood ornament, chrome elements on the grille, and split-style headlights. \",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S front design\",\"sequence\":2,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_113856_5ca5d41a.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S side profile\",\"caption\":\"Windowline and door handles have a chrome finish, and there's a golden emblem on the rear quarter panel.\",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S side profile\",\"sequence\":3,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_114122_788a96e5.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear design\",\"caption\":\"It gets T-shaped LED taillights with a glod-plated logo and two faux vents on the sides. \",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear design\",\"sequence\":4,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_114149_ba22832e.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S dashboard\",\"caption\":\"It sports 3-spoke steering wheel, dual digital screens and dual wireless phone chargers. \",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S dashboard\",\"sequence\":5,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_114429_8077fca3.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear seat view\",\"caption\":\"The dashboard, seatbacks, doors sport wooden elements to make it look luxurious and upmarket. \",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear seat view\",\"sequence\":6,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_114435_d30dd5ac.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear seats\",\"caption\":\"The rear seats are electrically adjustable and feature extendable leg rests and adjustable headrests.  \",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear seats\",\"sequence\":7,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false},{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_114449_ed92536e.jpg\",\"title\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear quarter\",\"caption\":\"The 800S will go on sale overseas in 2027 with a triple-motor AWD setup.\",\"alt_text\":\"Lac Hong 800S rear quarter\",\"sequence\":8,\"img_category\":\"Exterior\",\"use_as_thumbnail\":false}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-images/vinfasts-lac-hong-800s-image-gallery-440148\",\"author\":\"Dipan Sur\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Dipan-Sur-ACI-profile.jpg\",\"description\":\"\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-04T12:09:32.622077+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-04T12:09:33+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-04T13:54:38.703564+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"images_count\":8}],\"videos\":[{\"id\":439992,\"heading\":\"Karun Chandok on F1 India return prospects, 2026 F1 predictions and more\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_070334_95684d4d.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260304_070334_95684d4d.jpg\",\"title\":\"Karun Chandok F1 India \",\"caption\":\"\",\"alt_text\":\"Karun Chandok F1 India \"}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-videos/karun-chandok-on-f1-india-return-prospects-2026-f1-predictions-and-more-439992\",\"author\":\"Unnatee Gidithuri\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Unnattee_Mug_shot.png\",\"description\":\"14 years after it won the 2012 Indian GP, the Red Bull RB8 returned to the Buddh International Circuit, this time with Karun Chandhok behind the wheel. Chandok discusses what needs to fall into place for the Indian GP's return, likely pecking order for the upcoming 2026 F1 season, the Red Bull Moto Jam in Delhi-NCR and more.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-04T07:04:47.096067+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-04T07:04:56+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-04T07:04:57.285439+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6LK4QhPphXQ\"},{\"id\":439991,\"heading\":\"Celebrating 25 years of the Maruti Alto video\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260303_053835_4c15af7b.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260303_053835_4c15af7b.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"alt_text\":\"Maruti Alto\"}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-videos/celebrating-25-years-of-the-maruti-alto-video-439991\",\"author\":\"Shapur Kotwal\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/shapur.gif\",\"description\":\"The humble little Alto turned 25 this year, and we bring together every generation to celebrate a car that has given a lot of success to Maruti Suzuki.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-03T05:38:59.614913+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-03T05:39:11+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T05:39:12.177103+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xs29OtiV18w\"},{\"id\":439990,\"heading\":\"Mega Compact SUV Comparison Video \",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260302_143053_56806b6d.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260302_143053_56806b6d.jpg\",\"title\":\"Compact SUV comparison video \",\"caption\":\"\",\"alt_text\":\"Compact SUV comparison video \"}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-videos/compact-suv-mega-comparison-video-439990\",\"author\":\"Nikhil Bhatia\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/bhatiax.jpg\",\"description\":\"If you’re in the market for a new compact SUV, this video is for you. We have brought together 7 of the options available to you. The list includes the new Hyundai Venue, Skoda Kylaq, Kia Syros, Kia Sonet, Mahindra XUV 3XO, Tata Nexon and Maruti Suzuki Brezza. \",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-02T14:33:11.386500+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-02T14:33:21+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-02T14:34:09.288541+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"site_sub_category\":\"NA\",\"video_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eHhFbfwYADo\"},{\"id\":439989,\"heading\":\"Quick News video: March 1,2026\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260302_050447_fd4c20e7.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260302_050447_fd4c20e7.jpg\",\"title\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"alt_text\":\"Quick News\"}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-videos/quick-news-video-march-439989\",\"author\":\"Lenny D'sa\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Lenny_ACI.PNG\",\"description\":\"In this week’s Autocar India Quick News, Mercedes-Benz debuts the electric CLA in India, Isuzu updates the D-Max V-Cross and Mini opens bookings for the Cooper 1965 Victory Edition. Also, we have updates on the Renault Duster launch and the upcoming 350cc motorcycles from Triumph India.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-02T05:06:38.864218+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-02T05:06:39+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-02T05:06:38.867545+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"site_sub_category\":\"NA\",\"video_url\":\"http://youtube.com/watch?v=AurI6Kc35RE\"},{\"id\":439988,\"heading\":\"New Tata Sierra meets the OG video\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260301_113104_7c5c6604.jpg\",\"images\":[{\"url\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/image-galleries/images/20260301_113104_7c5c6604.jpg\",\"title\":\"New Tata Sierra meets old Tata Sierra video\",\"caption\":\"\",\"alt_text\":\"New Tata Sierra meets old Tata Sierra video\"}],\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-videos/new-tata-sierra-meets-the-og-video-439988\",\"author\":\"Shapur Kotwal\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/shapur.gif\",\"description\":\"The new Tata Sierra revives a legendary nameplate. What made the original an icon and how much of its DNA is in the new one? We connect the past and present on an epic drive from Tata’s Pune plant—where the original was built—to the Sanand plant that produces the new model.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-01T11:37:40.365343+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-01T11:37:40+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T11:37:40.368351+00:00\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"site_sub_category\":\"NA\",\"video_url\":\"https://youtu.be/wA8DQEGAvr4?si=wdNgopna3r9_Jl61\"}]},\"blogs\":[{\"id\":440298,\"heading\":\"Opinion: Taking a leaf out of the new Mercedes S-Class launch \",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/features/images/20260302_122821_187df0df.jpeg\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-blogs/opinion-taking-a-leaf-out-of-the-new-mercedes-s-class-launch-440298\",\"author\":\"Sergius Barretto\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Sergius_final.jpg\",\"description\":\"It seems the customer is always portrayed as God’s perfect creation.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-06T02:30:00.082967+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-06T02:30:00+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T02:30:00.141476+00:00\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\"},{\"id\":440289,\"heading\":\"Opinion: how retro design should be reinterpreted for modern times \",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/features/images/20260227_140328_7b2789b5.jpeg\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-blogs/opinion-how-retro-design-should-be-reinterpreted-for-modern-times-440289\",\"author\":\"Shapur Kotwal\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/shapur.gif\",\"description\":\"Go too retro, and you risk caricature. What you want is progress, not pastiche.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-01T02:30:00.126358+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-03-01T02:30:00+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T02:30:00.164487+00:00\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\"},{\"id\":440268,\"heading\":\"Opinion: What Nissan could have done better with the Gravite\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/features/images/20260222_050504_2cbbcba5.png\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-blogs/opinion-what-nissan-could-have-done-better-with-the-gravite-440268\",\"author\":\"Uday Singh\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Uday_Singh.JPG\",\"description\":\"Nissan's version of the Renault Triber arrives over six years after the latter was first launched.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-02-22T05:07:31.248997+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-02-22T05:07:31+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-23T03:42:32.269077+00:00\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\"},{\"id\":440213,\"heading\":\"Opinion: How Tata Motors has spearheaded technical innovations with CNG\",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/features/images/20260215_103250_dfe1f735.jpg\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-blogs/opinion-how-tata-has-spearheaded-technical-innovations-with-cng-440213\",\"author\":\"Uday Singh\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Uday_Singh.JPG\",\"description\":\"The Indian carmaker has shown that CNG cars can be feature-rich, pack good performance and offer usable boot space.\",\"published_at\":\"2026-02-15T05:30:12.153506+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-02-15T10:16:45+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-16T04:19:38.664063+00:00\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\"},{\"id\":440230,\"heading\":\"Who goes first? Maruti, Toyota and the great EV price mystery \",\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/features/images/20260214_164133_e991e73e.png\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-blogs/who-goes-first-maruti-toyota-and-the-great-ev-price-mystery-440230\",\"author\":\"Hormazd Sorabjee\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Hormazd_web.jpg\",\"description\":\"Months after the reveal of the Maruti Suzuki e Vitara and, more recently, the Toyota Urban Cruiser Ebella, both are in showrooms without a price tag. Is this delay a lack of conviction in India’s newest electric SUVs?\",\"published_at\":\"2026-02-14T09:44:44.455584+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-02-14T09:54:19+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-16T05:37:04.117004+00:00\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\"}],\"trendingArticles\":[{\"id\":419390,\"article_type\":\"news\",\"heading\":\"Top 10 cheapest 7 seater cars in India\",\"published_at\":\"2025-10-08T11:01:00+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-02-19T08:40:59+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-24T05:20:51.944378+00:00\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/car-news/top-10-cheapest-7-seater-cars-in-india-419390\",\"total_views\":358364,\"image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/ExtraImages/20251008043030_Cheapest_7_seater_cars_in_India.jpg\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"description\":\"Mahindra dominates this list with three SUVs.\",\"author\":\"Uday Singh\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Uday_Singh.JPG\"},{\"id\":438915,\"article_type\":\"news\",\"heading\":\"Mahindra issues statement on the BE 6 fire incident\",\"published_at\":\"2026-01-28T07:35:57.945322+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-01-28T07:35:58+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-01-29T13:45:39.533286+00:00\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/car-news/mahindra-issues-statement-on-the-be-6-fire-incident-438915\",\"total_views\":219637,\"image\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/news/images/20260129_134252_0e70e1ca.jpg\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"description\":\"All occupants of the midsize electric SUV are reportedly safe and unharmed.\",\"author\":\"Suraj Viswanathan\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Suraj-Viswanathan-ACI-profile.jpg\"},{\"id\":431936,\"article_type\":\"features\",\"heading\":\"Every car tested by Bharat NCAP so far\",\"published_at\":\"2025-12-03T06:28:00+00:00\",\"republished_date\":\"2026-01-21T08:55:48+00:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-17T04:37:41.547644+00:00\",\"article_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-features/every-car-tested-by-bharat-ncap-so-far-431936\",\"total_views\":182391,\"image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/ExtraImages/20251201121353_Every_car_tested_by_Bharat_NCAP_so_far%20_1_.jpg\",\"site_category\":\"Cars\",\"site_sub_category\":\"\",\"description\":\"Bharat New Car Assessment Program has crash-tested 29 models to date, including ICE-powered vehicles and EVs. \",\"author\":\"Uday Singh\",\"author_image\":\"https://img.autocarindia.com/staff/Uday_Singh.JPG\"}],\"initialCity\":\"delhi\",\"currentMagazine\":{\"magazine_id\":\"1544\",\"issue_number\":\"318\",\"display_name\":\"Autocar India: February 2026\",\"image_path\":\"https://asset.autocarindia.com/static/magazines/images/20260211_104349_b93c48a1.jpg\",\"description\":\"$1d\",\"is_current_issue\":true,\"sale_date\":\"2026-02-11T00:00:00.000Z\",\"edition_month\":2,\"edition_year\":2026,\"magazine_url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/magazine/issue/1544\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-11T10:44:18.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-11T10:44:18.000Z\",\"schema_published_date\":\"2026-02-11T00:00:00+00:00\",\"schema_modified_date\":\"2026-02-11T10:44:18.961588+00:00\",\"articles_in_issue\":[{\"type\":\"Feature\",\"title\":\"Suzuki Access 125: Generational Talent\",\"url\":\"https://www.autocarindia.com/auto-features/suzuki-access-125-generational-talent-440224\",\"published_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:00:38.000Z\"}]}}]}]\n"])</script></body></html>